{
  "texts": [
    "Fig. 4 shows the final prompt template used in RAGTAG.",
    "This template results from numerous internal experimentation and fine-tuning iterations among the first two authors.",
    "Context RetrievalOnce the prompt is generated, the next step is to retrieve the related context from the RAG pipeline (Fig. 2).",
    "The indexing step of RAG takes the domain documentation corpus as input with HTML, PDF, Microsoft document, or text files and splits it into passages (or chunks).",
    "The default chunk size is 512 tokens, and we use the default size in our implementation as this is typically large enough to provide context."
  ]
}